-- Oil & Natural Gas May Spend 40 Billion Rupees in Three Years to Buy Rigs
-- B y   R a k t e e m   K a t a k e y
-- 2010-09-23T06:47:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-23/oil-natural-gas-may-spend-40-billion-rupees-in-three-years-to-buy-rigs.html
Oil & Natural Gas Corp. may spend
40 billion rupees to buy 10 onshore rigs and four offshore rigs
in three years, U.N. Bose, director, said in an interview in New
Delhi today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
